---
const techStack = [
  { name: "React / Next.js", category: "Frontend" },
  { name: "Node.js", category: "Backend" },
  { name: "TypeScript", category: "Sprache" },
  { name: "MongoDB", category: "Datenbank" },
  { name: "Shopify API", category: "E-Commerce" },
  { name: "WhatsApp API", category: "Messaging" },
  { name: "Meta API", category: "Werbung" },
  { name: "AWS / Vercel", category: "Infrastruktur" }
];
---

<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="about-container">
    <!-- Split Layout -->
    <div class="about-grid">
      <!-- Left: Editorial Content -->
      <div class="about-content">
        <div class="content-label">
          <span class="label-number">05</span>
          <span class="label-text">Über mich</span>
        </div>

        <h2 class="about-title">
          Vom Operator zum
          <span class="title-accent">Automatisierungs-Architekten</span>
        </h2>

        <div class="about-body">
          <p class="lead">
            Nachdem ich Millionen in Meta Ads investiert und 7-stellige Funnels gebaut habe,
            entdeckte ich den wahren Hebel: Individuelle Software schlägt jede Marketing-Strategie.
          </p>

          <p>
            Ich war auf beiden Seiten—habe €100k+ tägliches Werbebudget verwaltet, Conversion-Raten
            optimiert, Retention-Strategien entwickelt. Aber die größten Erfolge kamen durch
            Automatisierung: WhatsApp-Flows, die die Retention verdoppelten, Zeiterfassungssysteme,
            die 15 Stunden wöchentlich sparten, individuelle Shopify-Apps, die Abläufe skalierten.
          </p>

          <p>
            Heute arbeite ich als technischer Mitgründer auf Abruf. Ich identifiziere die Engpässe,
            die dein Wachstum bremsen, und baue dann individuelle Lösungen, die den Output deines
            Teams vervielfachen. Jedes System, das ich baue, amortisiert sich in 3-6 Monaten.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Highlights -->
        <div class="about-highlights">
          <div class="highlight">
            <span class="highlight-label">Standort</span>
            <span class="highlight-value">Deutschland</span>
          </div>
          <div class="highlight">
            <span class="highlight-label">Arbeitsweise</span>
            <span class="highlight-value">Remote-first</span>
          </div>
          <div class="highlight">
            <span class="highlight-label">Kunden</span>
            <span class="highlight-value">Weltweit</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Photo + Tech Stack Card -->
      <div class="about-visual">
        <div class="about-image-wrapper">
          <img src="/images/fabian-profile.webp" alt="Fabian Eppinger" class="about-image" />
        </div>

        <div class="stack-card">
          <div class="stack-header">
            <span class="stack-label">Tech Stack</span>
            <span class="stack-year">2026</span>
          </div>

          <div class="stack-grid">
            {techStack.map((tech) => (
              <div class="stack-item">
                <span class="item-name">{tech.name}</span>
                <span class="item-category">{tech.category}</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background: #0c0c0c;
    padding: clamp(5rem, 12vw, 10rem) 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-container {
    max-width: 1800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 8rem);
  }

  .about-content {
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .content-label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .label-number {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #a7a9ac;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .label-text {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #ffffff;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #ffffff;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .title-accent {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    display: block;
  }

  .about-body { margin-bottom: 3rem; }

  .about-body .lead {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 1.5vw, 1.375rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about-body p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #a7a9ac;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-body p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .about-highlights {
    display: flex;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 4rem);
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .highlight {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .highlight-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #a7a9ac;
  }

  .highlight-value {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .about-visual {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 420px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-image-wrapper { width: 100%; }

  .about-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
  }

  .stack-card {
    background: #ffffff;
    padding: clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
  }

  .stack-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.875rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .stack-label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0c0c0c;
  }

  .stack-year {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: #a7a9ac;
  }

  .stack-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 0.5rem 1rem;
  }

  .stack-item {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.625rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .stack-item:hover .item-name { color: #0c0c0c; }

  .item-name {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #0c0c0c;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .item-category {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.5625rem;
    color: #a7a9ac;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .about-grid { flex-direction: column; gap: 4rem; }
    .about-visual { width: 100%; max-width: 500px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-highlights { flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .highlight { flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
    .stack-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
